</div>
</a>
</li>
<li id="masonry-list__item_1-0-6" class="comp masonry-list__item mntl-block">
<a id="mntl-card_1-0-6" class="comp is-inverted-small mntl-card card" data-doc-id="2353079" data-tax-levels href="https://www.thoughtco.com/current-situation-in-iran-2353079" data-cta="Read Now â–¸" data-ordinal="7">
